Parameters:
    Quiz data availability:
        ALL_QUIZ_DATA is empty.     [single] [property NoQuestions]
        ALL_QUIZ_DATA has entries.  [property HasQuestions]

    Name entry:
        Name parameter provided (non-None).                  [if HasQuestions] [property NameProvided, NameNotNone]
        Name parameter not provided; user enters blank -> None. [if HasQuestions] [property NameNone]
        Name parameter not provided; user enters non-blank.     [if HasQuestions] [property NamePrompted, NameNotNone]


    Number of questions requested:
        User enters valid integer in range.   [if HasQuestions] [property CountValid]
        User enters non-integer first (ValueError) then valid.  [if HasQuestions] [property CountValueErrorThenValid]
        User enters out-of-range first then valid.              [if HasQuestions] [property CountRangeErrorThenValid]

Environments:
    Question selection (random indices):
        Random shuffle produces distinct indices.  [if HasQuestions] [property IndicesDistinct]
        Random shuffle edge: request equals total_available. [if HasQuestions] [property CountEqualsTotal]

    Real answer normalization:
        Answer already uppercase A-D.   [if HasQuestions] [property AnswerUpper]
        Answer needs strip/upper.       [if HasQuestions] [property AnswerNormalized]

    Option formatting:
        Options list contains 4 choices A-D.  [if HasQuestions] [property FourOptions]

    Guess input validation loop:
        User guess valid immediately (A/B/C/D).          [if HasQuestions] [property GuessValidImmediate]
        User guess invalid then valid (loop repeats).    [if HasQuestions] [property GuessInvalidThenValid]

    Guess outcome per question:
        User picks the REAL correct answer (mistake).    [if HasQuestions] [property GuessEqualsReal]
        User avoids the real answer (scores +1).         [if HasQuestions] [property GuessNotReal]

    Summary and score:
        Mode score computed over all questions.          [if HasQuestions] [property SummaryPrinted]

    Score persistence:
        Name is None -> do NOT save.      [if NameNone]     [property NoSave]
        Name not None -> save percent score. [if NameNotNone] [property SaveScore]

